只是我以为钱会被送来，而不是被收走
I had it planned!

193
00:18:37,368 --> 00:18:40,162
Only the money should have been delivered, not taken away!

194
00:18:40,276 --> 00:18:44,132
都是那个他妈的杰克，给的错误资讯
That fucking Jack, downtown, he gave me the wrong information.

195
00:18:44,848 --> 00:18:48,339
杰克又是谁啊？幕后的策划人吗？
What is this Jack supposed to be? A mastermind or what?

196
00:18:49,551 --> 00:18:52,906
我们有难同当，我们必须离开这里
We're all in the barrel together and we want to get out of it.

197
00:18:56,157 --> 00:18:59,648
我需要时间思考，让我想想…
All right, I got to have time to think. I got to think.

198
00:19:17,976 --> 00:19:20,436
仔细听好，靠近这里一步
Keep away or we'll start throwing bodies out the door, one at a time. Got that?

199
00:19:20,476 --> 00:19:23,436
我就开始射杀人质一次一个，听到没？

200
00:19:26,617 --> 00:19:27,605
你是谁？
Who is this?

201
00:19:37,994 --> 00:19:39,585
有人叫珍妮吗？
Is there a Jenny here?

202
00:19:40,463 --> 00:19:42,123
谁是珍妮？
Who's Jenny here?

203
00:19:42,431 --> 00:19:43,624
我就是
That's me.

204
00:19:43,865 --> 00:19:46,162
是你这松鼠，有没有先生？
It's the squirrel. You got a husband?

205
00:19:46,835 --> 00:19:48,825
他在电话上
Well, he's on the phone.

206
00:19:49,104 --> 00:19:50,161
接啊
Go ahead.

207
00:19:51,806 --> 00:19:53,363
我要说什么？
What could I tell him?

208
00:19:53,974 --> 00:19:56,464
我不知道，随便你说啊，告诉他详情
I don't know, whatever. Tell him the truth.

209
00:19:56,677 --> 00:19:59,770
真是他妈的闹剧，WNEW，热门音乐电台
What a fucking comedy! W-N-E-W plays all the hits.

210
00:20:00,013 --> 00:20:01,502
听着，先别挂
Listen. Don 't hang up.

211
00:20:02,482 --> 00:20:04,870
里面有人受伤吗？　　没有
-First, is anybody hurt in there? -No.

212
00:20:05,118 --> 00:20:09,042
别靠近，不然我会一个个杀人质，听到吗？
Keep away or we'll start throwing bodies out, one at a time. You got that?

213
00:20:09,321 --> 00:20:12,847
别，等一下，让我跟你聊聊，里面有几个人？
Don't. Let me talk to you for a while. How many people you got?

214
00:20:13,158 --> 00:20:15,717
别问了，你再打给我，你等下再打给我
No, call me back.

215
00:20:14,548 --> 00:20:15,674
Call me back.

216
00:20:17,995 --> 00:20:20,087
他问你们几点会弄完？
He wants to know when you'll be through.

217
00:20:21,731 --> 00:20:23,789
什么？拜托你，小姐
What? Girlie, please!

218
00:20:32,141 --> 00:20:33,971
快上…
Come on. Let's go.

219
00:20:40,748 --> 00:20:43,375
后门在哪儿？　　里面锁住了
-Where's the back door? -It's locked on the inside.

220
00:20:43,551 --> 00:20:44,847
在哪儿？
Where is it?

221
00:20:45,053 --> 00:20:47,213
走廊底的右边
Through the passageway to the right.

222
00:20:49,156 --> 00:20:52,181
沙尔，掩护他们
Cover them!

223
00:20:52,526 --> 00:20:55,619
你随便煮嘛，什么都可以
You could just go ahead and look whatever's there.

224
00:21:27,089 --> 00:21:29,921
好，我会的，我会的
Oh, yes, I will. Yes, I will.

225
00:21:30,826 --> 00:21:33,350
喂，该挂了　　　亲爱的，我得挂了
-Let's go, come on. -Honey, I've got to go now.

226
00:21:34,395 --> 00:21:35,554
我得挂了
I got to go.

227
00:21:36,864 --> 00:21:38,353
我也爱你
I love you too.

228
00:21:39,233 --> 00:21:41,496
现在待在这里面
All right, inside here.

229
00:21:45,672 --> 00:21:47,559
我不知道发生什么事
I don't know what happened.

230
00:21:48,008 --> 00:21:51,238
可能有人不小心触动警报器
Maybe somebody tripped an alarm or something. I don't know.

231
00:21:51,510 --> 00:21:53,932
一定有办法逃出去的，放心好了
But there's a way out of this.

232
00:21:54,213 --> 00:21:57,477
你说的是真的吗？　　什么是真的？
-Were you serious about what you said? -About what?

233
00:21:58,016 --> 00:21:59,175
你真的要…

234
00:22:02,687 --> 00:22:05,450
你真的要射杀人质？
About throwing those bodies out the door?

235
00:22:08,191 --> 00:22:13,048
我只是放风声罢了　　　我只想确认一下
-That's what I want him to think. -I want to know what you think.

236
00:22:16,866 --> 00:22:20,096
因为我已经准备好了
Because I'll tell you right now, I'm ready to do it.

237
00:22:20,736 --> 00:22:22,896
是吗？好吧
Right. Okay.

238
00:22:23,338 --> 00:22:25,828
我是说真的　　　我知道
-I mean it. -I know.

239
00:22:29,443 --> 00:22:32,138
所有人听着，我们现在出了点问题
Listen, everybody. I know we got a problem here.

240
00:22:32,379 --> 00:22:35,142
但是别担心，很快就可以解决
But there's a way out of this thing. I'm telling you.

241
00:22:35,449 --> 00:22:37,973
只要跟我们合作
All you got to do is cooperate with me.

242
00:22:38,217 --> 00:22:42,880
保持镇定，快解决了，听话就不会有人受伤
Stay cool, and we'll get out of this.

243
00:22:40,945 --> 00:22:42,947
Nobody gets hurt if you listen to me.

244
00:22:43,189 --> 00:22:47,215
首先，一步一步来，你要去厕所对吧？
First, we'll do things a step at a time. You got to go to the bathroom, right?

245
00:22:47,492 --> 00:22:49,152
她可以去
She'll get to go to the bathroom.

246
00:22:49,394 --> 00:22:53,750
其他人也可以去，但我们要一起行动
Everybody who has to go is going. We'll do things together, okay?

247
00:22:54,165 --> 00:22:55,893
保持镇静，他怎么了？
What's the matter with him?

248
00:22:58,235 --> 00:23:00,896
他有气喘　　　气喘？
He's got asthma.

249
00:23:00,172 --> 00:23:01,465
Asthma?

250
00:23:15,784 --> 00:23:17,546
我来处理
I'll take care of that.

251
00:23:18,286 --> 00:23:19,411
你叫什么名字？
-You, what's your name? -Mulvaney.

252
00:23:19,587 --> 00:23:20,814
马维尼　　　马维尼？

253
00:23:21,122 --> 00:23:22,110
你跟我来
Come with me.

254
00:23:23,958 --> 00:23:26,949
他有气喘你们还要他当警卫？　　他上过警校
-He's got asthma and he's a guard? -They go to guard school.

255
00:23:27,160 --> 00:23:29,684
学怎么开枪吗？他连枪都没有
To learn how to shoot? He doesn't have a gun.

256
00:23:29,896 --> 00:23:32,989
他们早上升旗，一周可赚150元
They earn a $105 a week to fold the flag in the morning...

257
00:23:33,199 --> 00:23:35,359
我不知道他们学什么
...straighten up. I don't know what they learn.

258
00:23:35,701 --> 00:23:39,727
我要把门挡起来，以免他们冲进来
I want to block that door. In case they try coming in, I can hear it.

259
00:23:40,406 --> 00:23:41,702
过来帮我
Let's move this.

260
00:23:46,444 --> 00:23:48,206
等一下，等一下
Wait a minute. Hold it!

261
00:23:50,414 --> 00:23:51,778
先把这个拿走
Let's get rid of this.

262
00:23:57,987 --> 00:23:58,975
你有小孩吗？
You got kids?

263
00:23:59,222 --> 00:24:01,519
两个，我还想见到他们
I got 2 kids and I'd like to see them again.

264
00:24:01,691 --> 00:24:04,545
别担心，你会的，你一直都还蛮听话的
You'll see them again. You're being cooperative.

265
00:24:04,827 --> 00:24:07,488
我对你没有任何抱怨…没有抱怨…
I got no complaints against you, whatsoever.

266
00:24:08,363 --> 00:24:09,351
一点都没有
Whatsoever. You got bank insurance?

267
00:24:09,598 --> 00:24:11,792
你有没有银行保险？　　你知道我有

268
00:24:12,000 --> 00:24:14,365
你好像蛮清楚银行的事
You know I do. You seem to know a lot about bank procedure.

269
00:24:16,203 --> 00:24:17,931
我还知道很多事
I know a lot of things.

270
00:24:21,574 --> 00:24:24,701
我只是想让你们安全离开，不是吗？
I just want to get you out of here safe, right?

271
00:24:26,246 --> 00:24:27,906
如果我要你跟我走？
What if I take you with me?

272
00:24:28,615 --> 00:24:29,876
如果你要带人的话
If you take anybody...

273
00:24:30,182 --> 00:24:31,739
就选我吧
...please take me.

274
00:24:32,384 --> 00:24:33,941
他们会开枪射你，你知道？
They'll shoot you, you know?

275
00:24:34,253 --> 00:24:35,514
警察
The cops...

276
00:24:35,721 --> 00:24:39,611
他们根本不在乎银行什么保险，看看亚提卡…
...don't care about bank insurance. See what they did in Attica?

277
00:24:39,957 --> 00:24:43,778
他们杀了42人，不管有罪无罪…
42 people killed. The innocent with the guilty.

278
00:24:45,462 --> 00:24:46,485
总之放心

279
00:24:49,666 --> 00:24:52,395
我不会选你的，我要选女人
I won't take you. I'll take one of the girls, a married one with kids.

280
00:24:52,703 --> 00:24:54,329
结婚有小孩的

281
00:24:54,503 --> 00:24:57,391
警察要是杀了她们，见报就不好看了
Cops don't like it in the papers when they shoot a married woman with kids.

282
00:24:57,573 --> 00:24:58,664
尤其是有小孩的

283
00:25:02,410 --> 00:25:03,899
你还不错
You're all right.

284
00:25:05,180 --> 00:25:06,441
你不会跟我玩把戏吧
You won't fuck with me?

285
00:25:36,574 --> 00:25:38,165
调查局的人来了
There's the FBI.

286
00:25:41,778 --> 00:25:43,301
你好吗，沙登？
How you doing, Sheldon?

287
00:26:05,599 --> 00:26:08,226
你为什么不等他们出来呢？
Why didn't you wait and try to take them outside?

288
00:26:08,835 --> 00:26:09,994
我判断错误
An error in judgment.

289
00:26:10,303 --> 00:26:13,658
我以为他们看到警察、听到被包围会吓破胆
Thought the S.O.S would be remorseful at the sight of a policeman.

290
00:26:13,906 --> 00:26:14,929
而且…
And you know something?

291
00:26:15,808 --> 00:26:17,638
没人提及里面有人质
Nobody said "hostage" yet, okay?

292
00:26:20,979 --> 00:26:23,037
发生抢案了
We got a bank robbery here.

293
00:26:25,817 --> 00:26:28,376
记者是怎么突破封锁线的？
How did the press guys get through the barrier?

294
00:26:34,758 --> 00:26:37,988
这次的银行抢案没有任何资讯
We don't know what's up yet. We're setting up communications.

295
00:26:38,261 --> 00:26:41,684
我是CBS的布莱恩，请问现场的状况如何？
This is Ron Cummins from CBS. Can you tell me the situation?

296
00:26:42,098 --> 00:26:46,761
我们在架设通讯设备，嫌犯在里面
We're setting up communications. Our perpetrators are in the bank.

297
00:26:47,002 --> 00:26:48,525
我只能说那么多
That's all I can say now.

298
00:26:48,770 --> 00:26:51,101
有什么我会再跟你们说
When I get it, you'll get it. That's all.

299
00:26:53,307 --> 00:26:56,298
你们在逃生梯那儿干嘛？我是说屋顶
What are you doing on the fire escape?

300
00:26:56,477 --> 00:26:58,364
快上屋顶，可以吗？
I said on the roof. Get up on the roof, will you?

301
00:27:47,322 --> 00:27:49,846
叫电信局了吗？　　全架设完毕
-Get the phone company? -Setting it up now.

302
00:27:50,057 --> 00:27:52,479
这支电话能直接与银行里的人通话
This phone is going to be a direct line into the bank.

303
00:27:58,631 --> 00:28:02,191
我是马维尼　　　我是摩瑞提，让我跟他说话
-Mulvaney speaking. -Moretti here. Let me talk to him.

304
00:28:05,370 --> 00:28:07,860
什么事？　　我是尤金摩瑞提探长
This is Detective Sergeant Eugene Moretti.

305
00:28:10,342 --> 00:28:12,502
现在你们在里面，我们在外面，要怎么办
You're there, we're here. What do we do?

306
00:28:12,877 --> 00:28:14,901
我不知道怎么办
I don't know. What do we do?

307
00:28:15,346 --> 00:28:17,233
首先，我想知道人质都安全吧
Are the people in the bank okay?

308
00:28:17,715 --> 00:28:18,840
是的
They're okay.

309
00:28:19,149 --> 00:28:22,970
你自己一个人还是有同伙？　　我不是一个人
-You alone or you got confederates? -I'm not alone.

310
00:28:24,721 --> 00:28:28,076
还有沙尔　　　沙尔？全名是沙尔瓦多？
I got Sal.

311
00:28:26,165 --> 00:28:28,083
What's that for, Salvatore?

312
00:28:28,324 --> 00:28:29,756
沙尔是个杀手
He's a killer.

313
00:28:30,259 --> 00:28:33,455
我们参加过越战，杀人对我们来说小事一桩
We're Vietnam veterans. Killing don't mean anything to us.

314
00:28:33,996 --> 00:28:35,656
军队里？　　对
-In the army? -Yeah.

315
00:28:35,931 --> 00:28:37,659
你叫什么名字？
So you, what's your name?

316
00:28:38,432 --> 00:28:40,092
你为什么要知道我的名字？
Why do you want to know my name?

317
00:28:40,935 --> 00:28:42,856
我想有个名字称呼你
Just so I got something to call you.

318
00:28:51,111 --> 00:28:54,705
只是给个名字不会怎样的
Let's be reasonable, okay? Just give me your name.

319
00:28:56,682 --> 00:28:58,410
叫我桑尼吧　　　桑尼
Call me Sonny.

320
00:28:59,084 --> 00:29:00,607
听好，桑尼
Listen, Sonny.

321
00:29:00,919 --> 00:29:03,648
我想确认人质的安全　　　嗯
I want to see if the people are okay.

322
00:29:04,155 --> 00:29:06,714
然后我想要跟你商量释放人质的事
Right.

323
00:29:04,829 --> 00:29:07,373
Then I want to work out a way to get them out.

324
00:29:07,358 --> 00:29:09,313
等一下我会不带枪进去里面
I want to come over without a gun.

325
00:29:09,626 --> 00:29:12,719
你可以搜我身，取得你的信任之后
Frisk me so you'll trust me. We'll find a way out of this.

326
00:29:13,463 --> 00:29:14,451
好
I just want to find some way that I can trust you too.

327
00:29:14,665 --> 00:29:18,430
好的，那我该怎么相信你呢？要公平嘛，对不对？

328
00:29:18,935 --> 00:29:21,425
我可不想被枪扫射而死
Not be on the street where you could shoot me.

329
00:29:21,637 --> 00:29:24,002
一些信号？　　没错，像什么？
-Some sign, right? -Right. Like what?

330
00:29:25,073 --> 00:29:26,096
放人质出来如何？
Let the people out.

331
00:29:26,308 --> 00:29:29,970
等一下，你以为我是他妈的白痴啊？
Who do you think you're dealing with? A fucking idiot here?

332
00:29:30,245 --> 00:29:32,508
我才不会放我的护身符出去
They're keeping me alive. Let them out?

333
00:29:32,746 --> 00:29:36,602
干嘛不跟我谈，有话直说　　　好吧，好吧
Talk to me. Just talk to me straight. I'm ready to talk.

334
00:29:37,318 --> 00:29:38,477
那你把女的放出来
Give us the women?

335
00:29:38,752 --> 00:29:41,140
不行，我这儿就只有女的
No, I've got women. That's all I've got.

336
00:29:41,421 --> 00:29:43,809
那就放其中一个
Give me something. Give me one of them.

337
00:29:44,257 --> 00:29:46,247
你要一个干什么？　　公平交易啊
-One? -It's like a fair exchange.

338
00:29:46,426 --> 00:29:50,384
我不会带武器进去，但不会把我当人质吧？
I'll come over. I won't pack nothing, don't know if you'll take me hostage.

339
00:29:50,762 --> 00:29:52,058
表示咱们互相信任嘛
It's a sign of trust.

340
00:29:52,364 --> 00:29:55,526
我怎么跟你连络？　　拿起电话就可以跟我通话
-How do I call you back? -It's a direct line.

341
00:29:55,801 --> 00:29:57,722
拿起电话就可以跟我通话
Pick up the receiver and I'm here.

342
00:29:59,971 --> 00:30:01,267
他要一个人
He wants one.

343
00:30:05,508 --> 00:30:07,566
他，好吗？　　当然好
Him, right?

344
00:30:06,682 --> 00:30:07,766
Right!

345
00:30:08,345 --> 00:30:10,437
可以吗？　　好

346
00:30:10,714 --> 00:30:11,702
他出去
He goes.

347
00:30:17,052 --> 00:30:19,144
对方到底是何方神圣？
What are we dealing with here?

348
00:30:20,989 --> 00:30:23,479
你一定要这样跟着我吗？
You have to keep checking me out all the time?

349
00:30:24,092 --> 00:30:25,149
是的
Yeah.

350
00:30:30,564 --> 00:30:32,224
他需要钥匙
He'll need the keys.

351
00:30:32,766 --> 00:30:33,925
你有吗？
Got the keys?

352
00:30:35,836 --> 00:30:37,860
给他那一支就好，桑尼　　　好啦
Just the one, Sonny!

353
00:30:52,450 --> 00:30:54,781
别开枪，别开枪
Don't fire!

354
00:30:54,952 --> 00:30:56,179
你们在干嘛？
What are you doing?

355
00:30:56,453 --> 00:30:59,250
他是人质耶，让他走
That's a hostage!

356
00:31:00,357 --> 00:31:02,051
别开枪
Don't fire!

357
00:31:02,392 --> 00:31:03,449
别开枪
Hold your fire!

358
00:31:03,659 --> 00:31:05,546
我们决定让他先出来
We voted to send him out!

359
00:31:06,729 --> 00:31:08,958
他是人质之一！　　放开他！
-He's one of the hostages! -Get away from him!

360
00:31:09,398 --> 00:31:11,627
你们怎么搞的　　　他是人质之一
He's a hostage!

361
00:31:11,800 --> 00:31:15,257
他是人质之一，放开他，你们这是干嘛？

362
00:31:13,666 --> 00:31:15,584
What the hell's the matter with you?

363
00:31:15,670 --> 00:31:19,093
我才不管！离远点！离开
I don't give a fuck! Get out of here.

364
00:31:19,607 --> 00:31:22,131
别挡路，桑尼！等一下
Hey, Sonny! Wait a minute!

365
00:31:22,610 --> 00:31:25,032
桑尼！这就是你的不对
That was your fault, Sonny.

366
00:31:25,278 --> 00:31:27,768
我们之间不是有电话吗？
We had the communications set up here.

367
00:31:27,947 --> 00:31:30,369
我们有250个警察在外面
We're not set up properly, with 250 cops here.

368
00:31:31,117 --> 00:31:32,674
我们不知道，你在里面干什么！
