一旦离开就不能回头
If we leave the country, there's no coming back here.

542
00:43:55,101 --> 00:43:56,533
你知道我说什么吧？不能回头！
There's no coming back.

543
00:43:56,702 --> 00:43:59,067
想要跟谁说话
If there's anyone you want to talk to...

544
00:43:59,638 --> 00:44:01,662
想要跟谁说再见的话，要快
...you want to say goodbye to, do it now.

545
00:44:06,944 --> 00:44:08,069
没有
No.

546
00:44:10,748 --> 00:44:12,942
你有想去的国家吗？
Is there any special country you want to go to?

547
00:44:16,252 --> 00:44:17,582
怀俄明
Wyoming.

548
00:44:19,888 --> 00:44:22,685
那里不行，那不是个国家
No, Wyoming.... That's not a country.

549
00:44:23,992 --> 00:44:26,221
没关系，我来处理
That's all right. I'll take care of it.

550
00:44:49,315 --> 00:44:51,339
放下！听到没？
Put them down!

551
00:44:55,086 --> 00:44:57,349
放下！听到没？看，我什么也没带
Put them down! You hear that? What do I have?

552
00:44:58,256 --> 00:45:01,747
这里也没有，要不要看我的袖子？
See this here, look! I got nothing up my sleeve!

553
00:45:01,925 --> 00:45:05,849
这里也没有，要不要看我的口袋？
I got nothing here either! Want to see my pockets? Here!

554
00:45:06,029 --> 00:45:07,825
你不敢不带枪吧？
You need that gun, right!

555
00:45:10,032 --> 00:45:13,125
摩瑞提，叫他们把枪放下
Moretti! Tell them to put their guns down!

556
00:45:13,503 --> 00:45:16,892
嘿，你！看不懂吗？把枪放回枪袋去！

557
00:45:15,007 --> 00:45:16,467
Put it in your holster!

558
00:45:21,777 --> 00:45:23,471
把枪放下！
Put the guns down!

559
00:45:25,646 --> 00:45:29,001
懂吗？把枪放下！那是什么？
You know what it means to put a gun down? What's this?

560
00:45:29,617 --> 00:45:30,810
那是什么？

561
00:45:32,152 --> 00:45:34,574
谢谢！这就对了！
Right! Thank you very much!

562
00:45:34,754 --> 00:45:36,277
感激万分

563
00:45:36,489 --> 00:45:38,149
你们终于开窍了
You got it, right?

564
00:45:39,825 --> 00:45:42,349
你们终于开窍了，嘿，摩瑞提
You got it, baby! Hey, Moretti!

565
00:45:42,694 --> 00:45:44,490
都是你帮我的
You made it happen!

566
00:45:49,567 --> 00:45:51,557
玛利亚在里面
You got Maria in there!

567
00:45:54,438 --> 00:45:55,665
玛利亚！

568
00:45:57,207 --> 00:46:01,131
他里面有枪！玛利亚…
He's got a gun in there!

569
00:46:01,545 --> 00:46:04,035
玛利亚，玛利亚…

570
00:46:05,714 --> 00:46:07,305
把他带走
Get him the fuck out of here!

571
00:46:07,650 --> 00:46:10,573
老天啊！　　怎么会这样？

572
00:46:09,228 --> 00:46:10,855
How the hell did that happen?

573
00:46:10,753 --> 00:46:13,380
我有沙尔在里面　　　别紧张，别紧张
-I got Sal in there! -Take it easy!

574
00:46:13,555 --> 00:46:14,680
通知管区警察
Notify the precinct.

575
00:46:14,856 --> 00:46:16,413
他是谁？
Who the fuck is that?

576
00:46:16,891 --> 00:46:20,121
只是个西班牙小孩　　　玛利亚又是谁？
One of them Spanish kids.

577
00:46:20,427 --> 00:46:23,657
她被你关…　　沙尔要见桑尼，不然就要开枪了
-Who's Maria? -She's inside.

578
00:46:20,990 --> 00:46:23,951
Sal wants to see Sonny, says he'll shoot unless he does!

579
00:46:24,131 --> 00:46:27,156
他是认真的，桑尼，他是认真的！　　沙尔…
He's serious! Sonny, he means it!

580
00:46:27,733 --> 00:46:29,791
没关系，没关系
It's all right.

581
00:46:31,037 --> 00:46:32,469
没事了

582
00:46:35,007 --> 00:46:37,395
对不起　　　怎么发生的？
-I'm sorry. -How'd that happen?

583
00:46:37,576 --> 00:46:40,066
他女朋友是人质之一，你没事吧
You got his girlfriend in there. You okay?

584
00:46:40,212 --> 00:46:42,133
他想杀我
That fuck tried to kill me.

585
00:46:42,314 --> 00:46:45,771
他打了你好几下　　　我被打了好几下
-You look all squeezed out. -I am squeezed out!

586
00:46:45,950 --> 00:46:48,315
让我看看你的头
Let me see your head, all right?

587
00:46:48,485 --> 00:46:50,850
我在流血！　　让我看看…
-I'm bleeding! -Let me see it.

588
00:46:58,194 --> 00:47:01,549
还好，你想跟我说什么？
It's all right. You want to talk to me about something?

589
00:47:02,097 --> 00:47:03,825
刚有个人打电话来
Should've heard that phone call.

590
00:47:04,366 --> 00:47:06,458
一个疯子打来说，要杀死所有的人
Some creep calls up and says, "Kill everybody. "

591
00:47:07,035 --> 00:47:08,763
每个人都想杀死所有的人
Everyone wants to kill everyone.

592
00:47:08,936 --> 00:47:12,359
这种人到处都会有的，对吧　　　对啊
I think you're going to get assholes like that any how, right?

593
00:47:16,910 --> 00:47:19,571
跟你说…我有个提议
I want to talk to you. I got an offer.

594
00:47:20,881 --> 00:47:22,370
我想要一架直升机
I want a helicopter.

595
00:47:24,083 --> 00:47:27,313
还要可以带我去任何国家的飞机
And a jet to go wherever I want to go.

596
00:47:27,553 --> 00:47:29,918
所以小的不行，要大的那一种
So I don't want a little jet, I want a big one.

597
00:47:30,089 --> 00:47:33,353
有酒吧和钢琴的那种，我很可能会离开国家
One with a bar, a piano. Maybe I want to leave the country.

598
00:47:33,758 --> 00:47:37,318
我不知道直升机是否能来这儿
I don't know whether a helicopter would fit in here or not.

599
00:47:38,429 --> 00:47:40,055
我帮你查查看吧　　　可以停在屋顶上
I'll check it.

600
00:47:40,297 --> 00:47:43,857
不行，上面是柏油，停上去会垮的
-It could land on the roof. -That's asphalt, it'll break through.

601
00:47:44,368 --> 00:47:46,494
让我打电话问我上司好吗？
I'll call my superiors, you understand?

602
00:47:46,803 --> 00:47:48,963
让我…　　那干嘛不叫你上司来呢？
Why not bring your superiors here?

603
00:47:49,138 --> 00:47:52,163
让我直接跟他们谈，就不必透过你了
Why am I talking to you if you got to call superiors?

604
00:47:52,575 --> 00:47:55,202
我们有分歧　　　对，所以我要跟他们说
-We don't always see eye-to-eye. -Yeah, so I'll talk to them.

605
00:47:56,344 --> 00:47:57,742
我会打电话问问他们怎么说
I'll see what they say.

606
00:47:58,280 --> 00:48:02,602
我和他们谈谈，还有其他的要求吗？
I'll talk to them and ask them, all right?

607
00:48:01,193 --> 00:48:02,861
Anything else I can get you?

608
00:48:06,487 --> 00:48:08,875
我要你把我太太带来这儿
I want you to bring my wife down here.

609
00:48:09,957 --> 00:48:12,754
好，那你要给我们什么？　　你要什么？
-What do you give us? -What do you want?

610
00:48:12,926 --> 00:48:14,790
女人质
The women hostages.

611
00:48:16,262 --> 00:48:18,183
老天啊，跟你说话真累
There's no talking to you!

612
00:48:19,065 --> 00:48:21,328
不是说过吗？里面全是女的
I told you, that's all I got in there is women.

613
00:48:22,467 --> 00:48:24,832
你到底要不要谈判啊？
You going to talk to me or what?

614
00:48:26,471 --> 00:48:29,496
你答应我一个要求，我给一个人质
I give one hostage for each thing you give me, see?

615
00:48:29,707 --> 00:48:33,836
给我直升机放一个人质，给我飞机再放一个
The helicopter for a hostage. The jet for a hostage.

616
00:48:34,145 --> 00:48:38,171
带我太太来给你一个，其他人用飞机送回家
You give me my wife, I give you a hostage.

617
00:48:36,687 --> 00:48:38,897
Then the rest come home on the jet.

618
00:48:41,284 --> 00:48:43,376
我看他们能怎么做好吗？
I'll see what they'll do, all right?

619
00:48:43,619 --> 00:48:46,576
在这段期间你赶快选人质
In the meantime, pick out who you want to give us.

620
00:48:46,855 --> 00:48:49,550
还有你太太在哪里？
And tell me where your wife is, all right?

621
00:48:49,792 --> 00:48:54,182
我坐在这儿管我自己的事，我听到桑尼抢银行
I'm here minding my own business, I hear the transistor go "Sonny what?"

622
00:48:54,362 --> 00:48:56,386
我真不敢相信，我抱起孩子就跑
I can 't believe my ears! I grab the kids!

623
00:48:56,564 --> 00:49:00,329
我告诉你那个抢银行的人，绝对不是桑尼
I'm telling you, Sonny didn't do it. It ain't him to rob a bank!

624
00:49:00,500 --> 00:49:04,094
桑尼绝不会伤害，或威胁任何人…
It ain't him to steal or hurt anybody or do nothing wrong!

625
00:49:04,271 --> 00:49:07,000
从我认识他到现在，他从没做过坏事
He's never done wrong since the day I know him!

626
00:49:07,173 --> 00:49:09,595
前天晚上，我们在康尼岛时
Night before last we're at Coney Island. I see he keeps a loaded gun on the car!

627
00:49:09,775 --> 00:49:13,335
发现他买了一把有子弹的枪

628
00:49:13,512 --> 00:49:16,139
我现才知道，他的行为有多么疯狂
Things are adding up how crazy he's acting lately...

629
00:49:16,614 --> 00:49:19,878
都是受坏朋友的影响　　　我就看着他
...and in with a bad crowd. So I look at him.

630
00:49:20,118 --> 00:49:22,881
到床上去，他像疯了似的一直骂小孩
Get in bed. He's yelling at the kids like a madman.

631
00:49:23,154 --> 00:49:26,509
然后他突然叫我带小孩去玩，我不想去
Then he wants me to go in a kiddie ride. I don't want to go.

632
00:49:26,690 --> 00:49:29,214
他就一直吼，乖，宝贝，嘘…
He starts screaming at me.

633
00:49:29,626 --> 00:49:32,480
一直吼个不停
He's screaming and screaming.

634
00:49:32,762 --> 00:49:35,787
在车里我问他，桑尼，你要那把枪干嘛？
I say, "What are you going to do with the gun?"

635
00:49:35,965 --> 00:49:37,727
不会是杀我，把尸体丢到河里吧？
Shoot me and dump me in the river?

636
00:49:38,000 --> 00:49:40,991
我当时好害怕，我从不怕他的
I was scared of him. I never been scared of him.

637
00:49:41,336 --> 00:49:45,066
他妈妈说我们一天到晚打架，还惊动警察
His mother says we always fought. The cops was always at our house.

638
00:49:45,273 --> 00:49:48,366
有一次我在车子里，想用千斤顶打他
I hit him with a jack handle once in the car.

639
00:49:49,209 --> 00:49:51,403
却打到我自己
I didn't even hit him. I hit myself.

640
00:49:51,578 --> 00:49:53,772
全身到处都是瘀伤
You should've seen the bruise on my leg.

641
00:49:54,348 --> 00:49:57,236
他却只穿上衣服戴帽子出门去
He'd put on his hat and coat, he goes out the door.

642
00:49:59,886 --> 00:50:03,275
所以，我不相信是他做的
So they tell me he did it. But I don't believe it.

643
00:50:03,622 --> 00:50:07,113
瓦基克小姐，听我说，你必须到银行来一趟
Mrs. Wortzik, listen to me. They want you down at the bank.

644
00:50:07,292 --> 00:50:11,022
他的身体有可能会做，但他的头脑绝不可能
His body functions might've done it, but he himself, he didn't do it!

645
00:50:19,302 --> 00:50:23,624
亲爱的艾比我梦过掉到水里
"Dear Abby: Lately I've been dreaming about falling into water...

646
00:50:23,807 --> 00:50:27,071
无法接近水面
...and not being able to reach the surface.

647
00:50:27,242 --> 00:50:31,530
我呼吸困难，我惊醒后一身冷汗
I begin to breathe heavily and I wake up in a cold sweat.

648
00:50:31,714 --> 00:50:35,979
一个朋友说我的问题是因为性压抑
A friend tells me that my problem is one of sexual repression. "

649
00:50:36,918 --> 00:50:39,283
玛格莉特，你还好吧？
Margaret, are you all right?

650
00:50:57,737 --> 00:51:01,502
你有没有对里面的女孩做任何事？
Are you doing anything to any of those girls on there?

651
00:51:02,107 --> 00:51:03,664
又是他
He's back again.

652
00:51:09,680 --> 00:51:10,668
这是谁？
Who's this?

653
00:51:11,548 --> 00:51:14,880
桑尼…玛格莉特
Look at Margaret.

654
00:51:17,487 --> 00:51:19,477
她怎么了？
What's the matter with her?

655
00:51:19,956 --> 00:51:22,253
这里没有空气
There's no air in here.

656
00:51:25,927 --> 00:51:28,315
空调坏了吗？
What happened to the air conditioning?

657
00:51:33,601 --> 00:51:35,761
苏，我很抱歉
I'm sorry, Syl.

658
00:51:38,339 --> 00:51:41,762
空调在哪儿？　　地下室
Where's the air conditioning?

659
00:51:40,390 --> 00:51:41,850
In the basement.

660
00:51:46,279 --> 00:51:49,076
沙尔，我下去看看空调
I'll go check the air conditioning.

661
00:51:49,782 --> 00:51:52,477
很快就回来　　　桑尼！
I'll be right back.

662
00:51:57,688 --> 00:51:58,676
干嘛？

663
00:52:00,725 --> 00:52:03,147
我从没坐过飞机
I never been up in an airplane before.

664
00:52:08,165 --> 00:52:09,654
又怎样？
So?

665
00:52:11,500 --> 00:52:13,455
我是说…坐飞机跟坐车一样
I mean, it's safe. It's like a car.

666
00:52:13,702 --> 00:52:15,362
事实上，比车还安全
It's safer than a car.

667
00:52:18,307 --> 00:52:19,739
别害怕，沙尔
It's all right, Sal.

668
00:52:25,747 --> 00:52:27,668
我要去检查空调了
I'm going to go check it now.

669
00:52:53,070 --> 00:52:55,196
沙尔，他们从后面进来了
They're coming in the back!

670
00:52:55,539 --> 00:52:57,096
进去金库，快点
In the vault!

671
00:52:58,609 --> 00:53:01,907
回去，退回去　　　不，不要开枪
-Get back! -No, don't fire!

672
00:53:09,351 --> 00:53:10,374
桑尼，注意点
That's it, Sonny!

673
00:53:10,719 --> 00:53:12,242
带她进去，快进去
Get her in there!

674
00:53:16,491 --> 00:53:17,787
那枪是谁开的？
Who fired that shot?

675
00:53:19,757 --> 00:53:21,217
Pick her up and put her in.

676
00:53:23,129 --> 00:53:24,720
是谁开枪的？
Who fired?

677
00:53:26,266 --> 00:53:28,358
快点，动作快！
Come on! Move!

678
00:53:28,768 --> 00:53:29,825
好，抬腿
Okay, legs!

679
00:53:35,808 --> 00:53:37,206
桑尼！

680
00:53:38,310 --> 00:53:39,435
嘿，桑尼
Get the bullhorn!

681
00:53:39,711 --> 00:53:40,904
拿扩音器给我！

682
00:53:44,916 --> 00:53:45,939
桑尼！

683
00:53:50,354 --> 00:53:51,945
你拿到扩音器了吗？
You got that bullhorn?

684
00:53:57,493 --> 00:53:58,516
嘿，桑尼！

685
00:54:00,997 --> 00:54:02,361
出来吧，桑尼！
Come on out, Sonny!

686
00:54:04,266 --> 00:54:05,357
桑尼！

687
00:54:06,768 --> 00:54:07,859
妈的！这是我“最”需要的了
That's all I need.

688
00:54:10,305 --> 00:54:12,636
桑尼！　　桑尼…

689
00:54:12,907 --> 00:54:14,032
你去处理一下吧！
Take care of that, will you?

690
00:54:15,876 --> 00:54:17,069
桑尼，出来吧！
Come on out!

691
00:54:18,279 --> 00:54:19,768
你们安静点儿行不行啊！
Straighten that out, will you?

692
00:54:20,213 --> 00:54:21,201
桑尼！

693
00:54:21,915 --> 00:54:23,108
桑尼，出来吧！
Sonny, come on out.

694
00:54:25,785 --> 00:54:26,808
桑尼？

695
00:54:28,220 --> 00:54:29,345
桑尼！

696
00:54:33,458 --> 00:54:37,484
桑尼！　　王八蛋，你想害死那些人吗？
You son of a bitch, you want to get those people killed?

697
00:54:37,995 --> 00:54:39,427
出来吧，桑尼！

698
00:54:43,366 --> 00:54:44,764
桑尼，出来吧！

699
00:54:49,272 --> 00:54:50,602
现在就出来吧！
Come on out here, now.

700
00:54:53,943 --> 00:54:55,170
快出来吧！桑尼

701
00:54:55,611 --> 00:54:56,804
桑尼！

702
00:55:01,049 --> 00:55:02,140
桑尼！

703
00:55:05,253 --> 00:55:06,947
快出来吧，桑尼！

704
00:55:09,089 --> 00:55:10,487
我可以看到你了，出来吧
I see you, Sonny, come on!

705
00:55:11,291 --> 00:55:12,279
来吧

706
00:55:28,740 --> 00:55:30,297
你神经错乱啦？
What's the matter with you?

707
00:55:30,841 --> 00:55:33,138
什么？　　你在里面开什么枪啊？
-What? -Why'd you fire that shot in there?

708
00:55:33,310 --> 00:55:35,800
我们有两百五十个警察在这边！　　该死！
We got 250 cops here!

709
00:55:35,980 --> 00:55:37,674
那你们在后头搞什么鬼？　　别再里头乱来！
Fuck you! What were they doing back there?

710
00:55:37,982 --> 00:55:39,846
你到底在玩什么把戏？
What the hell's the matter with you?

711
00:55:40,149 --> 00:55:42,309
什么？　　我们还要不要谈判？
Are we dealing?

712
00:55:42,485 --> 00:55:44,349
他们想进来是不是？　　谁？
-They were trying to get in there? -Who?

713
00:55:44,754 --> 00:55:46,675
少来这套！你心里明白
Come on, you know who!

714
00:55:47,522 --> 00:55:49,648
这到底是怎么回事？　　你们这群蠢蛋
-What's going on? -You're full of shit!

715
00:55:49,825 --> 00:55:51,780
去后面看看发生什么事
Find out what's going on there!

716
00:55:51,960 --> 00:55:54,655
我真的不知道　　　你别装模作样了
-Honest to God, Sonny, I don't know! -Bullshit!

717
00:55:54,829 --> 00:55:56,716
通讯设备还没架好　　　鬼扯…
Communications aren't set up yet.

718
00:55:56,931 --> 00:55:59,319
找其他人来跟我谈吧　　　去你妈的！
Get someone to talk to me!

719
00:55:59,500 --> 00:56:01,421
叫别人来吧，我不想再跟你谈了
I'm not talking to you anymore.

720
00:56:01,769 --> 00:56:04,430
让我跟你谈吧？　　你这说一套做一套的人
-Let me talk to you. -You say this, you do that.

721
00:56:04,671 --> 00:56:07,059
他们在后面做什么？　　我也不知道
Why were they back there?

722
00:56:07,240 --> 00:56:10,538
是吗？你不知道，又在装了　　　那是突击队
I don't know!

723
00:56:07,301 --> 00:56:08,427
You're full of shit!

724
00:56:08,678 --> 00:56:10,512
-It's another force. -A tactical force!

725
00:56:10,710 --> 00:56:13,303
他们喜欢开枪及攀岩走壁
They like to shoot, climb through windows!

726
00:56:13,479 --> 00:56:16,504
没有你的下令，他们也可以蛮干吗？
They like that, right! Without your orders, right?

727
00:56:16,682 --> 00:56:18,239
是的！他们不听我的命令
Yes! Without my orders!

728
00:56:18,584 --> 00:56:20,073
我怎么知道你们不会从屋顶上冲进来？
You coming through the roof?

729
00:56:20,251 --> 00:56:23,447
因为我说不会！　　是吗？你说的全是放屁！
I tell you we won't.

730
00:56:21,479 --> 00:56:24,898
You're telling me a lot of things, but you're not doing them.

731
00:56:23,621 --> 00:56:26,544
我讲了什么？　　他们在干嘛？

732
00:56:25,148 --> 00:56:26,440
What were they doing?!

733
00:56:26,724 --> 00:56:29,647
我不知道　　　你不能回答我
-I don't know! -And you can't answer me.

734
00:56:30,093 --> 00:56:31,582
什么？　　你不能回答我
-You can't answer. -Yes, I can.

735
00:56:31,728 --> 00:56:34,252
我可以，后面再干嘛！　　那告诉我他们在干嘛？
So tell me what they were doing.

736
00:56:34,731 --> 00:56:37,324
我们没有通讯设备，所以我派人到后面去
No communications! I sent someone back there.

737
00:56:37,484 --> 00:56:42,409
若沙尔开杀戒，全都是你的错，不是我的
I got a guy in there who's going to kill somebody. That's your responsibility.

738
00:56:42,588 --> 00:56:46,284
等等，你的要求我们都办好了　　　是吗？
Wait a minute, hold on. We got everything you wanted.

739
00:56:46,459 --> 00:56:49,757
是的，我们找不到直升机，但有辆巴士
Can't get a helicopter, but a bus is coming.

740
00:56:50,229 --> 00:56:52,856
飞机在甘尼迪机场待命，好吗？
We got a jet coming into Kennedy, all right?

741
00:56:53,198 --> 00:56:54,255
可以吗？

742
00:56:54,700 --> 00:56:55,688
好吧？

743
00:56:57,336 --> 00:56:59,291
我们已经找到你太太
We got ahold of your wife.

744
00:56:59,839 --> 00:57:01,100
她现在正要赶过来这里
Your wife is coming.

745
00:57:01,573 --> 00:57:03,836
我们已找到你太太，她现在正要赶过来
We reached her and she's coming here.

746
00:57:04,310 --> 00:57:05,298
可以吗？
Where are you going?

747
00:57:05,511 --> 00:57:08,070
你要去哪？　　不去哪，我还是在这里…

748
00:57:07,180 --> 00:57:09,682
I'm right here. I thought we were going to talk.

749
00:57:08,715 --> 00:57:10,079
我以为我们要谈判的

750
00:57:10,349 --> 00:57:11,975
我也是，但我们还没有谈
I thought so, too. But we're not.

751
00:57:12,184 --> 00:57:13,946
我们现在谈　　　你们却想从后门闯进来
We're trying to get in the back door.

752
00:57:14,120 --> 00:57:15,950
你太太将在三十分钟内赶到这儿
Your wife will be here soon.

753
00:57:16,488 --> 00:57:17,476
可以吗？

754
00:57:17,791 --> 00:57:19,951
满意吗？　　他们为什么枪还指着我？
They're still pointing. They love it.

755
00:57:20,125 --> 00:57:21,318
把枪收好！
Holster that weapon! Holster it!

756
00:57:21,494 --> 00:57:22,653
收好！

757
00:57:22,996 --> 00:57:24,189
把枪收好！
Holster that weapon!

758
00:57:25,065 --> 00:57:26,429
你也是
You too!

759
00:57:28,702 --> 00:57:30,032
好了吧
All right, come on.

760
00:57:30,270 --> 00:57:32,396
怎样？　　你还想怎样？
-What? -What else do you want me to do?

761
00:57:32,604 --> 00:57:34,434
你是要我怎样？
How could you do any better?

762
00:57:35,441 --> 00:57:36,930
我们什么都答应你了
We got all you wanted.

763
00:57:37,076 --> 00:57:39,566
你的要求我都答应
I'll do anything I can to stop anything.

764
00:57:42,015 --> 00:57:43,174
你还需要其他东西吗？
Anything else?

765
00:57:43,516 --> 00:57:45,210
有　　　什么？
-Yeah. -What?

766
00:57:45,385 --> 00:57:48,114
里面的人饿了
I got some people in there that are hungry.

767
00:57:48,288 --> 00:57:50,778
可否给他们点食物？　　没问题，要什么？
-Can you get food? -What do you want?

768
00:57:51,091 --> 00:57:53,650
送些披萨进去，好不好？　　好啊！
-Want some pizzas? -Yeah, all right.

769
00:57:54,026 --> 00:57:55,049
嘿，卡麦

770
00:57:56,196 --> 00:57:57,685
送些披萨进去
Get some pizzas in.

771
00:57:58,264 --> 00:58:00,219
可不可以再来点啤酒？　　嗯…
Can we get some beer, you think?

772
00:58:00,399 --> 00:58:03,253
不好不好，还是汽水吧？
No beer. Let's keep it to soft drinks, all right?

773
00:58:03,436 --> 00:58:04,595
好吧？

774
00:58:04,770 --> 00:58:05,758
卡麦

775
00:58:06,106 --> 00:58:08,596
记得还要有可乐汽水
Some soft drinks too, okay? Cokes!

776
00:58:08,775 --> 00:58:10,696
还要什么吗？　　再来点阿斯匹灵吧！
-What else? -And some aspirin too.

777
00:58:10,910 --> 00:58:12,707
还要阿斯匹灵　　　有人不舒服
Some lady's not feeling well.

778
00:58:13,179 --> 00:58:14,372
没有了吧？
Anything else?

779
00:58:15,682 --> 00:58:19,139
还有…不准耍我！　　不会！我干嘛耍你？
Don't con me.

780
00:58:17,150 --> 00:58:19,526
I'm not! Why would I want to do that?

781
00:58:19,352 --> 00:58:23,048
我已经够烦的了，也不想自找麻烦
I'm in trouble enough as it is. I'm not trying to create any trouble.

782
00:58:24,023 --> 00:58:25,148
好吧！

783
00:58:32,866 --> 00:58:34,059
没事了
It's okay.

784
00:58:38,238 --> 00:58:40,934
直升机没办法停在这儿
They can't bring a helicopter in here.

785
00:58:41,407 --> 00:58:43,294
沙尔，直升机没办法停在这儿
They can't land it here.

786
00:58:43,676 --> 00:58:47,031
他们要换一辆大巴士，可容纳我们全部
They're going to get us a big bus so we can all get in.

787
00:58:47,213 --> 00:58:49,203
接我们去机场
And that's how we get to the airport.

788
00:58:50,484 --> 00:58:52,075
目前情况还不错
It looks good.

789
00:58:54,854 --> 00:58:58,050
还有我刚帮你们叫了些吃的
You people, I just ordered you some food.

790
00:58:59,092 --> 00:59:01,286
也有阿斯匹灵
I even got her some aspirins.

791
00:59:01,461 --> 00:59:02,950
一切都进行得很顺利
So we're moving it along now.

792
00:59:03,831 --> 00:59:07,288
对了！我还得付食物钱，那些做记号的五元钞在哪？
I got to pay for the food. Where's the marked fives?

793
00:59:07,468 --> 00:59:10,164
你刚做了件愚蠢的事
That was a foolish thing you did back there.

794
00:59:12,305 --> 00:59:13,828
愚蠢的事？
Foolish thing.

795
00:59:17,511 --> 00:59:19,535
我们还要继续这样下去？
We going to get the ball rolling?

796
00:59:19,712 --> 00:59:22,202
对啊！不然你以为我在干嘛？
Yeah, what do you think I'm doing?

797
00:59:22,348 --> 00:59:24,474
事情一直在进行
I'm working on it. What's it look like?

798
00:59:24,652 --> 00:59:27,142
你以为这是件简单的事？我不能激怒他们
You think it's easy? I got to keep them cool.

799
00:59:27,321 --> 00:59:29,151
还要顾到你们
I got to keep you people happy.

800
00:59:29,322 --> 00:59:31,551
我想点子又谈判，都是我一人在做
I got to have the ideas and do it all alone.

801
00:59:31,725 --> 00:59:33,680
我在努力了，你想试试吗？
You want to try it?

802
00:59:33,860 --> 00:59:35,520
桑尼，你要的食物来了
Your food is here, Sonny.

803
00:59:37,765 --> 00:59:39,891
我开始讨厌你了
You're starting to get on my nerves.

804
00:59:49,410 --> 00:59:52,708
跟着他进去，不会有事的
Go on with him there. You'll be all right. Go right ahead.

805
00:59:55,783 --> 00:59:58,376
多少钱？　　付过了，已经付过了
-What do I owe you? -It's all paid for.

806
00:59:58,552 --> 01:00:01,816
没关系，我来付　　　有零钱
-No, I've paid for that. -I got it.

807
01:00:01,989 --> 01:00:03,285
拿去
Here.

808
01:00:03,456 --> 01:00:04,786
零钱留着
Keep the change.

809
01:00:11,732 --> 01:00:13,096
你想要这个
You want this?

810
01:00:17,171 --> 01:00:18,159
你们喜欢？
You like it?

811
01:00:28,617 --> 01:00:30,675
摩瑞提，要不要？
Moretti, could you use five?

812
01:00:39,026 --> 01:00:41,220
还有很多
I got a lot for you.

813
01:00:52,007 --> 01:00:53,633
退后，该死的！
Get back, god damn it!

814
01:01:11,726 --> 01:01:14,387
还要…
More! More! More!

815
01:01:24,105 --> 01:01:26,265
可以帮我开门吗？
Could you open it?

816
01:01:27,542 --> 01:01:28,940
谢了
Thank you, man.

817
01:01:33,681 --> 01:01:35,910
我成了明星！
I'm a fucking star!

818
01:02:00,108 --> 01:02:01,096
踢

819
01:02:01,576 --> 01:02:03,770
往上，翻转

820
01:02:04,044 --> 01:02:07,570
抱她起来，她不会有事的
No, just pick her up and hold her. She'll be okay.

821
01:02:09,117 --> 01:02:10,879
你踢得不错嘛！
You kick good. Here.

822
01:02:20,195 --> 01:02:21,286
踢！

823
01:02:22,130 --> 01:02:23,118
往上！
This is where it gets stuck!

824
01:02:23,398 --> 01:02:25,195
就是在这里卡住的

825
01:02:30,338 --> 01:02:33,135
她在愚弄自己
Miriam's making a fool of herself.

826
01:02:34,642 --> 01:02:37,940
谁有烟？　　我有
Anybody got a cigarette? Yeah, I do.

827
01:02:38,246 --> 01:02:39,735
你不是不抽烟？
Sylvia, you don't smoke!

828
01:02:41,950 --> 01:02:43,473
你不抽烟？
You don't?

829
01:02:44,686 --> 01:02:45,674
不抽

830
01:02:47,322 --> 01:02:49,277
那你现在干嘛抽？
Why do you want to start now?

831
01:02:49,625 --> 01:02:52,855
我快吓死了，你不抽烟吗？
-I'm scared to death, that's why. -You don't smoke?

832
01:02:53,396 --> 01:02:55,283
不抽　　　为什么？
No. How come?

833
01:03:00,436 --> 01:03:02,733
我不想得癌症　　　我的天啊！
-I don't want the cancer. -My God!

834
01:03:03,172 --> 01:03:04,729
把烟给我吧
The cigarette.

835
01:03:04,907 --> 01:03:06,567
爱抽就抽吧
Do what you want.

836
01:03:08,209 --> 01:03:10,597
我只觉得应该照顾自己的身体
I think you ought to take care of your body.

837
01:03:10,812 --> 01:03:12,676
我的身体？为什么？
My body? What for?

838
01:03:15,718 --> 01:03:17,708
身体是上帝的庙宇
Your body is the temple of the Lord.

839
01:03:20,890 --> 01:03:22,151
你是认真的？
You're serious!

840
01:03:25,226 --> 01:03:27,181
你可以抢银行
So you rob a bank...

841
01:03:27,363 --> 01:03:30,422
但不能沾恶习，是这样的吗？
...but you keep your body pure. Is that it?

842
01:03:35,904 --> 01:03:37,734
你到底要不要抽？
You going to smoke or what?

843
01:03:40,076 --> 01:03:41,372
要！
Yes.

844
01:03:41,544 --> 01:03:44,205
如果我因此得癌症，你得负一半的责任
If I die of cancer, it'll be half your fault.

845
01:03:49,552 --> 01:03:51,212
不，那是因为你意志力薄弱
No, it's because you're weak.

846
01:03:51,554 --> 01:03:53,214
是的！我意志力薄弱
Right, I'm weak.

847
01:03:55,791 --> 01:03:57,052
你的子弹呢？
Where's your bullets?

848
01:03:57,226 --> 01:03:58,715
我是马维尼…
Mulvaney speaking.

849
01:04:01,630 --> 01:04:03,062
是摩瑞提
It's Moretti.

850
01:04:08,170 --> 01:04:10,558
喂　　　你们千万不要轻举妄动
Will you guys hold it down back there?

851
01:04:10,774 --> 01:04:12,571
桑尼，你太太来了
They're bringing in your wife.

852
01:04:30,259 --> 01:04:32,624
摩瑞提在哪儿？　　可能在酒吧里
-Where's Moretti? -Probably in the bar.

853
01:04:41,138 --> 01:04:42,695
在理发厅里
In the barber shop.

854
01:04:45,541 --> 01:04:46,700
这是什么？
What's that?

855
01:04:47,977 --> 01:04:50,069
我们在你说的地址找到他
We went to Bellevue where you told us...

856
01:04:50,247 --> 01:04:51,736
他说是他太太
...said he was his wife.

857
01:04:51,915 --> 01:04:53,779
在教堂结婚的
They were married in a church.

858
01:04:53,950 --> 01:04:55,382
天啊！
Jesus Christ!

859
01:04:55,885 --> 01:04:57,181
礼昂！

860
01:05:00,723 --> 01:05:01,780
礼昂！

861
01:05:02,958 --> 01:05:04,584
礼昂！在这儿
Leon, over here!

862
01:05:05,060 --> 01:05:06,924
礼昂…

863
01:05:08,031 --> 01:05:09,395
礼昂，我在这边

864
01:05:10,466 --> 01:05:11,625
礼昂！
Happy birthday!

865
01:05:11,935 --> 01:05:13,231
生日快乐！

866
01:05:23,246 --> 01:05:25,338
让让　　　小心他的头…
-Give us some room. -Watch his head!

867
01:05:30,152 --> 01:05:31,641
他是同志？
He's a queer?

868
01:05:32,655 --> 01:05:34,918
探长，他找你
Sarge, he wants you!

869
01:05:36,426 --> 01:05:39,280
我不要这保护罩，拿走！
Get the shield out of here. I don't need it now.

870
01:05:39,629 --> 01:05:41,994
要的时候都不会出现
Where were you 4 hours ago, when I needed it?

871
01:05:42,165 --> 01:05:44,689
他们不会开枪的，桑尼，什么事？
He's not going to shoot. Yeah, Sonny, what?

872
01:05:44,968 --> 01:05:47,231
怎么了？他还好吧？
What happened? Is he all right?

873
01:05:47,404 --> 01:05:48,597
他只是有点头昏罢了
He's a little groggy.

874
01:05:48,772 --> 01:05:52,730
让我跟他说话　　　我等下叫他打电话给你
No, let me talk to him.

875
01:05:50,995 --> 01:05:53,205
I'll get him on his feet and call back.

876
01:05:53,510 --> 01:05:54,737
把门关上
Shut the door!

877
01:05:57,214 --> 01:06:00,273
安静点，我不想听到任何噪音
Stop the noise. I don't want to hear a fucking sound!

878
01:06:00,684 --> 01:06:02,082
打字机！
Typewriter!

879
01:06:02,252 --> 01:06:03,980
挂电话！
Get off the fucking phone.

880
01:06:04,721 --> 01:06:06,449
快点！
Now!

881
01:06:06,823 --> 01:06:08,551
给我些水！
Give me some water.

882
01:06:11,328 --> 01:06:12,487
礼昂

883
01:06:13,597 --> 01:06:14,585
礼昂
You all right? They give you a shot down at the hospital or something?

884
01:06:14,764 --> 01:06:18,460
你还好吧，礼昂？医院是不是帮你打针了？

885
01:06:19,636 --> 01:06:20,727
我的天啊！
They shot me with, like, unreal!

886
01:06:20,937 --> 01:06:22,858
一针打下去我整个人都昏了

887
01:06:23,039 --> 01:06:25,029
你可要振作点！
You got to get ahold of yourself...

888
01:06:25,208 --> 01:06:28,131
你待会儿还得劝他走出银行
...so you can talk to him, and see if he'll come out.

889
01:06:28,712 --> 01:06:29,837
我不知道
He's got 8 people there, with a Sal. You know him?

890
01:06:30,213 --> 01:06:32,737
里面有八个人，还有个叫沙尔的认识吗？

891
01:06:33,183 --> 01:06:36,345
不太认识　　　他说他要杀死这八个人
-No, not really. -He says he's going to shoot them.

892
01:06:36,653 --> 01:06:40,281
我…帮不上忙的，我不能阻止他
I can't help it. I can't stop him from anything.

893
01:06:40,457 --> 01:06:42,117
他不听你的听谁的？
Who will he listen to, then?

894
01:06:42,292 --> 01:06:45,419
我没办法跟他说，他不会听任何人的话
I can't talk to him. He won't listen to anybody.

895
01:06:45,595 --> 01:06:48,085
他整个夏天都怪怪的
He's been crazy all summer.

896
01:06:49,800 --> 01:06:51,630
六月的时候他就想杀我了
He's tried to kill me since June.

897
01:06:53,136 --> 01:06:56,491
他用枪指着我的头，用刀割我
He put a gun to my head. And he cut me with a knife.

898
01:06:56,673 --> 01:06:59,664
还打我朋友　　　你有试过叫警察吗？
-He beat up my friends. -Did you contact the police?

899
01:07:00,444 --> 01:07:02,172
有什么用？
What good would that do?

900
01:07:02,513 --> 01:07:06,471
他会更生气，他们阻止不了他的
It'd just make him mad. They don't know him. It wouldn't stop him.

901
01:07:06,651 --> 01:07:10,438
总得有人阻止他　　　你不懂，他疯了！
-Somebody's got to stop him. -You don't understand. He's crazy.

902
01:07:15,126 --> 01:07:16,752
他有老婆、小孩
He's got a wife, children.

903
01:07:17,861 --> 01:07:19,452
是个好爸爸
He's a wonderful father.

904
01:07:20,998 --> 01:07:22,055
他的妈妈…
His mother...

