01:20:59,123 --> 01:21:00,419
他说什么？
What'd he say?

1080
01:21:02,993 --> 01:21:05,119
他只是告诉我他们的计划
He was just talking about arrangements.

1081
01:21:05,296 --> 01:21:08,526
我有告诉他电视的事，别担心
I talked to him about the TV. It will be all right.

1082
01:21:09,233 --> 01:21:11,655
就这样？　　对
That's all?

1083
01:21:13,871 --> 01:21:15,394
那他为什么不在这儿说？
Why couldn't he say it here?

1084
01:21:17,107 --> 01:21:22,362
我不知道！他想给我看车子要打哪儿进来
I don't know. He wanted to show me how the bus is going to come in.

1085
01:21:32,656 --> 01:21:33,679
怎么了？
What's the matter?

1086
01:21:34,859 --> 01:21:36,985
去倒杯水！
Someone get a glass of water.

1087
01:21:39,264 --> 01:21:40,252
有没有手帕？
Got a hankie?

1088
01:21:42,266 --> 01:21:43,459
他们在披萨里下毒！
They poisoned the pizza.

1089
01:21:43,634 --> 01:21:45,225
不是啦！
It's not the pizza!

1090
01:21:45,402 --> 01:21:47,164
他有糖尿病！
He's got diabetes.

1091
01:21:48,239 --> 01:21:52,299
他刚有喝可乐，别给他吃东西，我来拿
He had some Coke before. Don't give him anything. I'll hold it.

1092
01:21:52,644 --> 01:21:55,840
需要我们帮忙吗，马维尼先生？
What can we do for you, Mr. Mulvaney? Tell us.

1093
01:22:00,450 --> 01:22:02,542
这里有没有医生？
Is there a doctor out here?

1094
01:22:05,722 --> 01:22:07,780
我们需要一个医生
We need a doctor in here.

1095
01:22:10,662 --> 01:22:12,185
我们需要一个医生
We need a doctor.

1096
01:22:14,598 --> 01:22:16,792
怎么了？　　经理有糖尿病
What?

1097
01:22:16,968 --> 01:22:18,366
他不太舒服
The manager, he's diabetic. He don't look good.

1098
01:22:32,116 --> 01:22:33,605
我要搜身
I got to search you.

1099
01:22:52,237 --> 01:22:53,396
只准他进来
Just him.

1100
01:22:54,939 --> 01:22:56,030
桑尼

1101
01:22:57,575 --> 01:23:01,396
我已经说服礼昂跟你说话，他现在在电话上
I've convinced Leon to talk to you. He's on the phone now.

1102
01:23:15,226 --> 01:23:16,715
他要接了
He's coming on.

1103
01:23:25,571 --> 01:23:26,696
喂？

1104
01:23:27,672 --> 01:23:28,729
喂？

1105
01:23:29,407 --> 01:23:30,771
喂？礼昂？
Hello, Leon?

1106
01:23:31,142 --> 01:23:32,199
喂？
Hello, Sonny.

1107
01:23:32,443 --> 01:23:34,137
喂？桑尼

1108
01:23:34,313 --> 01:23:35,870
怎么了？
What happened?

1109
01:23:36,047 --> 01:23:38,435
你…还好吧？
How are you doing?

1110
01:23:38,616 --> 01:23:41,345
嗯，我出院了
Well, I'm out of the hospital.

1111
01:23:41,553 --> 01:23:45,181
我知道，我以为你永远也不能出院
Yeah, I know. I thought you'd never get out.

1112
01:23:47,225 --> 01:23:50,113
我没想过会是这样出院的　　　是啊
I never thought I'd get out this way, I'll tell you.

1113
01:23:51,563 --> 01:23:53,154
你还好吧？
How are you doing?

1114
01:23:55,234 --> 01:23:57,394
我在发抖　　　是吗？
I'm a little shaky.

1115
01:23:57,569 --> 01:24:01,095
摩瑞提说你不想跟我说话
Moretti told me that you were all drugged up...

1116
01:24:02,107 --> 01:24:03,905
我想可能是你吃药的关系
...so I figured that's why you didn't want to talk. I was wondering why.

1117
01:24:03,907 --> 01:24:06,805
我刚还在想为什么你不想跟我说话

1118
01:24:06,979 --> 01:24:08,468
对啊，那里好糟糕
It was really terrible, you know?

1119
01:24:08,681 --> 01:24:12,036
一进去他们就认定你疯了
You walk in, and right away they say you're crazy.

1120
01:24:12,217 --> 01:24:15,413
然后就开始帮你打针，我的意思是…
Then they start sticking things in your arm.

1121
01:24:15,754 --> 01:24:19,541
你一天到晚昏昏沉沉，病怎么好得起来？
How do they expect you to get uncrazy if you're asleep all the time?

1122
01:24:21,126 --> 01:24:24,014
我才刚刚开始清醒
I'm just starting to come out of it now.

1123
01:24:25,197 --> 01:24:27,084
嗯　　　嗯
So, how are you?

1124
01:24:27,533 --> 01:24:30,660
你好吗？　　我很好

1125
01:24:29,302 --> 01:24:30,678
I'm fine.

1126
01:24:32,771 --> 01:24:34,465
这个场面有点扯吧？
This is something, huh?

1127
01:24:37,876 --> 01:24:40,070
是啊…

1128
01:24:41,179 --> 01:24:44,341
我不知道礼昂…我就快死在这儿了
I don't know. I'm dying here.

1129
01:24:44,983 --> 01:24:46,381
我快死了

1130
01:24:48,320 --> 01:24:51,584
听听你自己说“快死了”的德性？
You ever listen to yourself when you say, "You're dying"?

1131
01:24:51,757 --> 01:24:54,748
你听听你自己！　　你在说什么？
-You ever listen to yourself? -What are you talking about?

1132
01:24:54,960 --> 01:24:58,417
你这话是什么意思？什么你快死了
What do you mean, what am I talking about? "You're dying. "

1133
01:24:58,597 --> 01:25:01,485
你知道你每天都跟我说，你快死了吗？
Do you know that you say that to me every day?

1134
01:25:02,835 --> 01:25:05,826
不是你快死了，是你在杀死你身边的人
You're not dying. You're killing the people around you.

1135
01:25:06,004 --> 01:25:09,564
礼昂，别这样好不好？不要跟我废话
Leon, don't give me that shit. I don't need that deep shit now!

1136
01:25:09,742 --> 01:25:12,266
我想你可能不知道，这话是什么意思
You don't realize what the things you do mean.

1137
01:25:12,444 --> 01:25:15,105
是吗？我很清楚
Yeah?

1138
01:25:13,795 --> 01:25:15,128
I know what I do.

1139
01:25:15,481 --> 01:25:17,209
你用枪指着别人的头
You stock a gun to somebody's head.

1140
01:25:17,416 --> 01:25:19,576
我有时不知道自己在做什么　　　对
I don't know what I'm doing sometimes.

1141
01:25:19,753 --> 01:25:21,242
很明显的你不知道
Obviously, you don't.

1142
01:25:21,388 --> 01:25:24,117
“睡吧，礼昂，这样我扣扳机时就不会痛”
"Go to sleep so it won't hurt when I shoot. "

1143
01:25:24,590 --> 01:25:27,581
你以为我在医院里做啥？
What do you think I've been doing on the hospital?

1144
01:25:27,761 --> 01:25:31,252
我吃药是为了离开你，对吧？　　是啊
I take a handful of pills to get away from you.

1145
01:25:32,198 --> 01:25:34,757
结果我现在又和你通电话
Now I'm talking to you on the phone again.

1146
01:25:34,934 --> 01:25:37,731
我没有工作，没有朋友
I've got no job. I don't have friends.

1147
01:25:37,903 --> 01:25:40,564
我必须要跟人接触才活得下去
I can't live. I have to live with people.

1148
01:25:42,474 --> 01:25:44,361
对不起，你老是把死挂在嘴边，我听不下去了
This death business, I'm sorry.

1149
01:25:44,543 --> 01:25:47,773
我不知道我为什么要在这忍受你这堆废话
I don't know what I'm getting here with that shit.

1150
01:25:47,946 --> 01:25:52,143
你要我怎么回答？事情已经发生了
What am I supposed to say to that? This is going on.

1151
01:25:52,317 --> 01:25:54,807
你居然说这种话　　　对不起！
-You're giving me that shit. -I'm sorry.

1152
01:25:54,953 --> 01:25:56,510
你知道我现在的处境
You know what's happening.

1153
01:25:56,722 --> 01:25:59,451
你该知道我受的压力很大，你知道的！
You know the pressures I've been having, right?

1154
01:25:59,625 --> 01:26:02,980
你知道我的这些压力…你在医院里…
I got these pressures. You know it. You're in that hospital...

1155
01:26:03,162 --> 01:26:06,426
全身插满了管子，又想动变性手术，对吧？
...with them tubes coming out and want that operation, right?

1156
01:26:06,599 --> 01:26:09,158
你跟我说了一堆废话，大家都给我气受
You're giving me that shit. Everybody's giving me shit.

1157
01:26:09,334 --> 01:26:14,191
每个人都要钱，你要我就帮你　　　对
Everybody needs money. So you needed money? I got you money.

1158
01:26:14,374 --> 01:26:16,000
可是我没叫你去抢银行啊
I didn't ask you to rob a bank!

1159
01:26:16,176 --> 01:26:18,905
我知道你没要我去…
I know you didn't ask me.

1160
01:26:19,446 --> 01:26:22,642
我并不怪任何人
I'm not putting this on anybody, you know?

1161
01:26:22,815 --> 01:26:25,703
我不怪任何人，因为我是出于自愿的
Nothing on nobody! I did this on my own. You see?

1162
01:26:25,885 --> 01:26:29,012
你搞清楚了吗？我只是想让你知道…
All on my own, I did it. But I want you to know something.

1163
01:26:29,522 --> 01:26:32,251
我绝对能逃得出去
I want you to know that I'm getting out of here.

1164
01:26:32,892 --> 01:26:34,916
我会坐飞机离开这个地方
I'm getting a plane out of here...

1165
01:26:35,195 --> 01:26:38,925
我只是想让你知道而已，我要你来这儿…
...and I just wanted you to know it. And I wanted you to come down...

1166
01:26:39,399 --> 01:26:42,196
只是…想跟你说拜拜
...and I wanted to just say goodbye to you.

1167
01:26:42,402 --> 01:26:45,997
或是你也可以跟我一起走
Or, if you wanted to, you could come with me.

1168
01:26:46,173 --> 01:26:48,936
你可以自己决定，这就是我想讲的了
You're free to do what you want. That's what...

1169
01:26:49,117 --> 01:26:50,910
...I wanted to say to you.

1170
01:26:53,213 --> 01:26:55,601
我可以自己决定？　　对
-I'm free to do what I want? -Right.

1171
01:26:55,782 --> 01:26:58,639
我花了6个月时间试着离开你
I try to get away from you for months and I'm going with you on a trip?

1172
01:26:58,682 --> 01:27:00,639
现在却要我跟你一起离开？

1173
01:27:00,820 --> 01:27:02,980
你要去哪儿？
Where are you going?

1174
01:27:03,157 --> 01:27:07,217
我还不知道，之前是说去阿尔及利亚
I don't know where yet. We said Algeria. I don't know.

1175
01:27:07,393 --> 01:27:09,519
可能是去阿尔及利亚吧
So I'll go to Algeria. I don't know yet.

1176
01:27:09,696 --> 01:27:12,255
为什么选阿尔及利亚？
Why are you going to Algeria?

1177
01:27:13,766 --> 01:27:16,825
我不知道，那里有一家强森饭店
I don't know why. They got a Howard Johnson's there.

1178
01:27:18,071 --> 01:27:20,495
你疯了，知道吗？你真的疯了！
You're warped, you know that? You're really warped.

1179
01:27:20,511 --> 01:27:22,495
我真的疯了！我知道
I'm warped. I know I'm warped.

1180
01:27:22,709 --> 01:27:24,835
天啊！阿尔及利亚…
Algeria!

1181
01:27:27,914 --> 01:27:31,269
他们带着面具走路，头上又有怪东西
You know they walk around with masks on, things on their heads.

1182
01:27:31,451 --> 01:27:34,715
那边都是些疯子　　　那我该怎么办？
-They're a bunch of crazy people. -What am I supposed to do?

1183
01:27:34,888 --> 01:27:38,084
你可以选个好一点的地方　　　哪儿？
-You could have picked a better place. -Like where?

1184
01:27:38,259 --> 01:27:40,453
瑞士还是丹麦？
Sweden? Denmark?

1185
01:27:42,563 --> 01:27:44,655
对啊，那里不错
Yeah, like that.

1186
01:27:46,633 --> 01:27:49,795
沙尔想去怀俄明州
You know what? Sal wanted to go to Wyoming.

1187
01:27:49,970 --> 01:27:54,167
天啊！那不是个国家，他不知道怀俄明在哪
I had to tell him it's not a country. He don't know where Wyoming is.

1188
01:27:54,441 --> 01:27:56,536
我和不知怀俄明在哪的人一起打劫
I'm with a guy who don't know where Wyoming is. Think you got problems?

1189
01:27:56,541 --> 01:27:58,036
有问题的人不只是你！

1190
01:28:01,615 --> 01:28:03,412
那么…沙尔跟你一起
So, Sal is with you?

1191
01:28:03,583 --> 01:28:04,708
喔我的天！
Oh, boy!

1192
01:28:04,885 --> 01:28:07,045
我看你们还是投降得好
You'd be better off giving up.

1193
01:28:08,087 --> 01:28:11,476
我不会投降的，不然我何苦做这一切？
I'm not giving up, because why have I done this so far?

1194
01:28:11,658 --> 01:28:15,616
事情已经做到这个地步，现在何必投降？
I've gone so far with this, and why should I give up now?

1195
01:28:15,796 --> 01:28:17,558
我怎么能投降？
I can't give up.

1196
01:28:20,434 --> 01:28:24,130
你可以帮我个忙吗？　　什么忙？
-Would you do me a favor? -Yeah, what?

1197
01:28:26,473 --> 01:28:29,202
带我来这里的人
These guys that have me down here...

1198
01:28:31,445 --> 01:28:34,641
他们认为我是同谋
...they think I'm part of the plot to rob the bank.

1199
01:28:34,815 --> 01:28:38,602
怎么可能？太疯狂了
That's crazy, Leon. That's crazy. They're bullshitting you.

1200
01:28:38,786 --> 01:28:40,673
他们在唬你，想要耍你
They're giving you a snow job.

1201
01:28:40,854 --> 01:28:43,515
他们的确说我是共犯　　　才不是…
They told me I was an accessory.

1202
01:28:43,691 --> 01:28:46,579
他们胡说八道，别相信
That's just a con job on you. Don't listen to that.

1203
01:28:46,760 --> 01:28:50,786
我一定得听他们的…我在监狱里会活不下去
I have to listen to it. I can't survive in prison, Sonny.

1204
01:28:50,965 --> 01:28:53,762
礼昂，你不可能会坐牢的　　　你怎么知道？
-You're not going to prison. -How do you know?

1205
01:28:53,934 --> 01:28:55,696
我就是知道，你不会坐牢的
Because I know. Believe me.

1206
01:28:55,869 --> 01:28:58,359
拜托…告诉他们　　　拜托什么？
Look, please, just tell them.

1207
01:28:58,539 --> 01:29:00,028
告诉他们什么？
Tell them what?

1208
01:29:00,207 --> 01:29:02,128
告诉他们你我不是一伙的？
That you didn't do it?

1209
01:29:02,309 --> 01:29:05,539
他们现在在听电话吗？
Are they on the phone now?

1210
01:29:05,713 --> 01:29:06,701
对
Yeah.

1211
01:29:06,880 --> 01:29:09,211
好极了！礼昂，真是好极了
That's great, Leon. That's really terrific.

1212
01:29:09,416 --> 01:29:12,077
你跟我通话，还让他们监听，你可真聪明
You talk with them on the phone. Really smart!

1213
01:29:12,419 --> 01:29:14,374
我是被逼的　　　什么意思？
-I have no choice! -What do you mean?

1214
01:29:14,556 --> 01:29:18,514
你要我怎么办？我身边有七万多个警察围着
What am I supposed to do? There are 7,000 fucking cops all around me.

1215
01:29:18,860 --> 01:29:20,850
谁在听电话？　　不要怪在我头上
-Who's on now? -Don't lay it on me!

1216
01:29:21,028 --> 01:29:23,724
我没有怪你！可你知道他们在搞鬼吧？
I'm not, but you knew that was going on, right?

1217
01:29:23,964 --> 01:29:26,261
讲什么我怪你，你一定知发生什么事
You knew what was happening, right?

1218
01:29:26,433 --> 01:29:28,093
没错…可是我…
Yeah!

1219
01:29:28,268 --> 01:29:30,497
我只想知道谁在听电话？
I want to know who's on the phone now.

1220
01:29:32,507 --> 01:29:35,134
摩瑞提？摩瑞提，是你吗？
Moretti, is that you?

1221
01:29:36,276 --> 01:29:37,469
喂？

1222
01:29:39,681 --> 01:29:42,478
总有人说说话啊，他们还在听吗？
Will somebody talk to me? Somebody going to talk to me or what?

1223
01:29:43,051 --> 01:29:44,415
他们还在听吗？
They on now?

1224
01:29:44,986 --> 01:29:46,783
他们不会跟你说话的
They won't talk to you.

1225
01:29:47,087 --> 01:29:49,243
好吧，他没参与这次的计划
He didn't do it, okay? He had nothing to do with it.

1226
01:29:49,287 --> 01:29:52,043
他跟这件事一点关系都没有

1227
01:29:52,260 --> 01:29:53,283
可以了吧？
Will you get off the phone?

1228
01:29:53,528 --> 01:29:56,018
你们可以挂了吧？他们挂了吗？

1229
01:29:55,300 --> 01:29:56,051
Are they off?

1230
01:30:00,501 --> 01:30:01,489
嗯
That really convinced them. They wanted to know. Did I do it for you?

1231
01:30:01,670 --> 01:30:03,402
他们应该相信你了吧

1232
01:30:03,420 --> 01:30:06,402
这是他们要知道的，我帮你洗清罪名

1233
01:30:06,574 --> 01:30:08,734
谢谢你
Yeah, thanks. Thank you very much.

1234
01:30:10,745 --> 01:30:13,110
你现在要怎么办？
So now what? What are you going to do?

1235
01:30:13,281 --> 01:30:15,271
我想…
I thought...

1236
01:30:16,618 --> 01:30:18,778
我想我会回去医院
...that I would go back to the hospital.

1237
01:30:18,953 --> 01:30:23,241
他们人很好，也有心要帮我
They're really nice there. They seem like they're trying to help me.

1238
01:30:23,425 --> 01:30:26,018
你已经找到你要的东西了
That's good, then. You found something.

1239
01:30:26,494 --> 01:30:28,825
我也不太确定
I don't know if I have or not.

1240
01:30:30,765 --> 01:30:32,322
所以…你还是会去动手术吧？
Are you still going to have the operation?

1241
01:30:32,701 --> 01:30:35,032
会呀，当然会
Yeah!

1242
01:30:35,970 --> 01:30:39,029
我还应该跟你说什么？
So then, what am I supposed to say to you?

1243
01:30:45,580 --> 01:30:46,841
谢谢你
Thanks a lot...

1244
01:30:48,918 --> 01:30:50,145
还有…祝你一路顺风
...and bon voyage.

1245
01:30:51,453 --> 01:30:54,341
有缘再见面　　　是啊
Yeah, right. See you sometime.

1246
01:30:54,789 --> 01:30:56,551
我会在梦里见到你的
I'll see you in my dreams.

1247
01:30:56,725 --> 01:30:58,851
我会写首歌的
Right, I'll write a song.

1248
01:31:02,564 --> 01:31:06,260
知道吗…人生有时真有趣　　　你说过很多次了
