01:44:28,376 --> 01:44:30,764
你无法了解…
You don't understand...

1418
01:44:33,549 --> 01:44:35,379
我的言语
...the things I said...

1419
01:44:36,919 --> 01:44:38,283
和行为
...and did.

1420
01:44:41,390 --> 01:44:44,017
我就是我，我与众不同
But I'm me and I'm different.

1421
01:44:50,666 --> 01:44:53,156
我希望能有个军队仪式葬礼
I want a military funeral...

1422
01:44:58,072 --> 01:45:01,336
我有权要求免费下葬
...and I'm entitled to have one, free of charge.

1423
01:45:08,517 --> 01:45:09,744
愿上帝保佑你
God bless you...

1424
01:45:12,020 --> 01:45:13,577
看顾你…
...and watch over you...

1425
01:45:17,593 --> 01:45:20,186
直到我们再相会
...till we are joined in the hereafter.

1426
01:45:35,310 --> 01:45:37,834
我来签名
Here, I'll sign. I'll spell that last name.

1427
01:45:43,920 --> 01:45:45,045
小心
Watch out!

1428
01:45:45,487 --> 01:45:48,011
小心…

1429
01:45:52,862 --> 01:45:54,749
别这样嘛！探长，一张照片就好
Come on, Sarge, just one picture?

1430
01:46:02,471 --> 01:46:04,131
退后！退后！
Back, back!

1431
01:46:33,803 --> 01:46:35,758
你是司机？　　是的
You the driver?

1432
01:46:38,775 --> 01:46:40,605
我想检查一下
I want to check it out.

1433
01:46:44,947 --> 01:46:47,574
这椅子可以拿下来？　　不行，固定住了
Seats come out?

1434
01:46:46,401 --> 01:46:47,568
They're bolted.

1435
01:46:55,191 --> 01:46:57,954
好吧！灯从那边照过来
All right, here. Light me on that side.

1436
01:46:59,429 --> 01:47:00,452
照那边
Over there.

1437
01:47:13,875 --> 01:47:16,240
啊，你就是那个男的
You're the man, huh?

1438
01:47:17,580 --> 01:47:19,968
我刚看到报导
I was watching. I saw you, man!

1439
01:47:21,484 --> 01:47:24,543
你应该看看，你不会相信
You should see yourself, you wouldn't believe it!

1440
01:47:24,721 --> 01:47:26,210
我相信
I believe it.

1441
01:47:26,389 --> 01:47:27,821
但是席拉绝不会相信的
Sheila won't!

1442
01:47:28,192 --> 01:47:30,056
谁是席拉？　　我妈
-Who? -My old lady!

1443
01:47:30,226 --> 01:47:33,524
他们打电话来，叫我到公园西路258号
They said, "Gas up a stretch, go to 285 Prospect Park West. "

1444
01:47:33,696 --> 01:47:35,060
灯光照过来点
Give me some light over here.

1445
01:47:36,099 --> 01:47:38,862
我以为又是一堆…从按摩院出来的客人
I said, "Shit, another load from the massage parlors! "

1446
01:47:56,285 --> 01:47:57,444
没问题了
It's okay.

1447
01:47:57,721 --> 01:47:59,881
我一定会记得你
I'm going to remember you.

1448
01:48:06,996 --> 01:48:09,589
这是墨飞探员，他来开车
This is Agent Murphy. He'll be your driver.

1449
01:48:09,966 --> 01:48:11,330
不，我要他
No, I want him.

1450
01:48:13,503 --> 01:48:16,596
我要这个黑人　　　我才不要这浑水
-Give me the black guy. -I'm not into that shit.

1451
01:48:16,873 --> 01:48:18,134
别这样，没人会伤害你的
Nobody will hurt you.

1452
01:48:19,041 --> 01:48:21,929
没有人会被杀，要杀早杀了，还等现在？
If they were going to shoot, they would've shot already.

1453
01:48:22,146 --> 01:48:24,739
我不答应　　　你不答应？
-I can't allow that, Sonny. -You can't allow?

1454
01:48:25,081 --> 01:48:28,436
你谁啊？这里我下命令
What makes you think you can say shit to me? I'm running this.

1455
01:48:29,987 --> 01:48:31,817
我会付钱的，你要多少，一百元？
I'll pay you. What do you want? $100? $200?

1456
01:48:31,989 --> 01:48:34,479
两百元？一千元？怎样？
$1,000? Come on.

1457
01:48:35,559 --> 01:48:37,514
别看他，我才是老大
Don't look at him, I'm running this.

1458
01:48:38,829 --> 01:48:40,125
来嘛！

1459
01:48:42,165 --> 01:48:43,654
会很好玩喔
Look, it'll be an adventure.

1460
01:48:49,238 --> 01:48:52,365
要杀杀白人，别杀我
You men that shoot, aim for white meat.

1461
01:49:00,651 --> 01:49:01,708
你走吧
Take a walk.

1462
01:49:03,887 --> 01:49:04,875
我要他
Give me him.

1463
01:49:07,223 --> 01:49:09,554
你以为你在跟白痴谈判啊？
Think I'm an idiot?

1464
01:49:11,195 --> 01:49:12,559
滚，条子！
Take a walk, cop!

1465
01:49:17,768 --> 01:49:19,962
大家都想耍老千
Everybody is a con man.

1466
01:49:25,042 --> 01:49:26,770
我要所有人都到对面去
I want everyone across the street.

1467
01:49:28,545 --> 01:49:30,967
退到对面去
I want them all back, on the sidewalk!

1468
01:49:31,281 --> 01:49:33,009
快呀
Let's go!

1469
01:49:33,317 --> 01:49:35,910
至少我知道我面对的人是谁
At least I know who I'm dealing with now.

1470
01:49:38,789 --> 01:49:40,813
这支笔给你
Here's a pen for you. Come on!

1471
01:49:51,435 --> 01:49:53,265
站在这儿别动
Don't move, okay?

1472
01:49:57,007 --> 01:49:59,861
桑尼，你的文件
Here's your document.

1473
01:50:01,511 --> 01:50:03,842
谢谢　　　你必须签名
-Thanks. -You've got to sign it!

1474
01:50:06,517 --> 01:50:07,949
准备走了
We're taking off.

1475
01:50:08,119 --> 01:50:09,813
我们要走了
We're going now.

1476
01:50:10,088 --> 01:50:12,476
沙尔，他在哪儿？沙尔…
Sal! Where is he?

1477
01:50:12,856 --> 01:50:14,049
沙尔

1478
01:50:14,292 --> 01:50:16,316
就这样，我们要上路了
That's it, we're going.

1479
01:50:16,861 --> 01:50:18,953
各位，要上路了
Here, people, let's go! We're going.

1480
01:50:19,597 --> 01:50:23,521
我可以拿我的毛衣吗？　　拿你该拿的
-Can I get my sweater? -Get what you had when you came in.

1481
01:50:33,211 --> 01:50:34,199
沙尔

1482
01:50:37,048 --> 01:50:38,036
沙尔

1483
01:50:41,185 --> 01:50:42,515
你还好吧？
How are you doing?

1484
01:50:42,686 --> 01:50:43,913
还好　　　还好？
Good.

1485
01:50:44,088 --> 01:50:46,578
我们要上路了，好吗？
We're going to do it, right?

1486
01:50:46,724 --> 01:50:48,782
我们要上路了，沙尔，你看
We're going to do it.

1487
01:50:48,960 --> 01:50:51,656
注意看着他，他是司机
You got to keep your eye on him. He's the driver.

1488
01:50:51,829 --> 01:50:54,160
我需要这把枪　　　不，这是我的
-I need it. -No, it's mine.

1489
01:50:54,532 --> 01:50:56,761
你要看好这小子
You got to keep your eye on him, see?

1490
01:51:01,606 --> 01:51:03,493
现在怎么办？
All right, where am I now?

1491
01:52:01,032 --> 01:52:02,555
等一下
All right, hold it!

1492
01:52:04,236 --> 01:52:06,226
好了，可以走了
All right, let's go.

1493
01:52:06,404 --> 01:52:08,769
转过来…
Swing around now.

1494
01:52:10,141 --> 01:52:11,938
手不要放开
Just keep holding hands.

1495
01:52:18,283 --> 01:52:19,306
等一下
Hold it!

1496
01:52:21,652 --> 01:52:23,812
数到三就放手，还不要放手…
Break it on "3. " Not yet, don't break it.

1497
01:52:24,723 --> 01:52:25,711
一

1498
01:52:26,625 --> 01:52:27,613
二

1499
01:52:28,293 --> 01:52:29,384
三，进车子里
Go!

1500
01:52:40,873 --> 01:52:42,999
我们成功了！
Fuck, we did it!

1501
01:52:43,242 --> 01:52:44,435
我们成功了！
We did it!

1502
01:52:44,643 --> 01:52:45,904
祝我们好运！
Wish us luck!

1503
01:52:47,980 --> 01:52:49,003
再见

1504
01:52:50,949 --> 01:52:52,381
我放了一人质了
You got your one.

1505
01:52:53,018 --> 01:52:54,279
跟着我的车
Follow my car.

1506
01:53:06,865 --> 01:53:09,162
帮我接甘尼迪机场　　　沙尔…
Get me Kennedy.

1507
01:53:09,768 --> 01:53:11,132
沙尔，我们成功了！
We did it!

1508
01:53:13,172 --> 01:53:15,731
我们成功了！
I'll be a son of a bitch! We did it!

1509
01:53:15,908 --> 01:53:19,138
按喇叭，我们走吧！
Okay, let's move. Come on, honk the horn.

1510
01:53:21,648 --> 01:53:23,945
沙尔，帮个忙
Do me a favor, will you?

1511
01:53:24,116 --> 01:53:27,073
把枪指别的地方，如果路上颠簸，枪容易走火
Keep the gun pointed up. We hit a bump, it'll go off.

1512
01:53:37,429 --> 01:53:38,690
你们好了吗？
You set out there?

1513
01:53:42,235 --> 01:53:44,032
我们要准备离开这儿
We're leaving now.

1514
01:53:44,403 --> 01:53:46,290
一路上不准有任何的麻烦
We want no trouble en route.

1515
01:53:49,174 --> 01:53:50,470
路口都安排好了？
Intersection check?

1516
01:53:53,179 --> 01:53:55,203
好…我们现在就要出发
We'll be starting up right now.

1517
01:53:55,380 --> 01:53:56,676
10－4
10-4.

1518
01:54:28,648 --> 01:54:30,046
会没事的
It'll be all right.

1519
01:54:56,042 --> 01:55:00,536
沙尔，你一定要记得要把枪口向上

1520
01:54:57,816 --> 01:55:00,818
You just have to remember to keep the gun pointed up.

1521
01:57:27,628 --> 01:57:28,958
他在那里干嘛？
What's he doing?

1522
01:57:29,363 --> 01:57:31,785
他在安排事情
He's still got some arrangements to make.

1523
01:57:45,180 --> 01:57:46,203
就是这架？没错！

1524
01:57:47,682 --> 01:57:50,411
沙尔，看到没？就是那架飞机
Sal, see it? There it is.

1525
01:58:47,276 --> 01:58:48,936
糟糕
I forgot!

1526
01:58:49,110 --> 01:58:51,304
我忘了问上面有没有吃的
I forgot to ask if they got food on board.

1527
01:58:56,152 --> 01:58:57,550
上面会有食物吗？
Do they have food on board?

1528
01:59:04,193 --> 01:59:05,352
看，那就是你要求的飞机
Your jet.

1529
01:59:05,527 --> 01:59:08,290
人质呢？我们约定好的　　　对
We get one more now. That's the deal.

1530
01:59:09,063 --> 01:59:11,951
好，谁要走？　　苏菲雅？
Right. Okay, who goes?

1531
01:59:10,674 --> 01:59:11,759
Sylvia?

1532
01:59:13,501 --> 01:59:14,489
玛莉亚！
Maria.

1533
01:59:22,811 --> 01:59:24,801
我会帮你们祷告的
I'll pray for you.

1534
01:59:25,681 --> 01:59:26,772
沙尔

1535
01:59:27,683 --> 01:59:29,946
第一次坐飞机…
Because this is your first plane trip...

1536
01:59:30,119 --> 01:59:32,541
不要太害怕
...don't be scared, okay?

1537
01:59:46,235 --> 01:59:49,362
我刚才想起我一整天都没吃，飞机上会有食物吗？
I didn't eat all day. Will there be any food on board?

1538
01:59:49,537 --> 01:59:51,697
飞机上有汉堡，准备好了吗？
There'll be hamburgers. Ready?

1539
01:59:54,510 --> 01:59:56,773
沙尔　　　怎样？

1540
01:59:57,079 --> 01:59:58,102
要走了喔
Ready to go?

1541
01:59:59,347 --> 02:00:00,438
好啊
Yeah.

1542
02:00:06,554 --> 02:00:07,850
好，我们走吧
Let's move.

1543
02:00:09,792 --> 02:00:11,019
沙尔

1544
02:00:12,061 --> 02:00:15,188
我们不想这时候出意外
We don't want any accidents at this point, right?

1545
02:00:15,598 --> 02:00:17,360
记得把枪口朝上
Keep your gun pointed up.

1546
02:00:19,635 --> 02:00:22,592
你要第一个出来吗？　　我准备好了
Ready to get out first?

1547
02:00:21,854 --> 02:00:22,729
Ready.

1548
02:00:28,110 --> 02:00:29,098
别射我
Don't shoot me.

1549
02:01:08,083 --> 02:01:09,572
手脚张开
Now spread them!

1550
02:01:15,358 --> 02:01:17,052
我们已处理完了
We're all secure here.

1551
02:01:17,227 --> 02:01:19,786
墨飞会在车子里报告
Murphy will report from the car.

1552
02:01:24,601 --> 02:01:26,295
你来报告
You make the report.

1553
02:01:26,469 --> 02:01:27,958
把枪收起来
Put the gun down.

1554
02:01:28,138 --> 02:01:29,832
退后
Back off.

1555
02:01:30,272 --> 02:01:32,193
起来，桑尼
Get up now, Sonny.

1556
02:01:32,875 --> 02:01:34,364
你被逮捕了
You're under arrest.

1557
02:01:34,511 --> 02:01:36,740
你有权保持沉默
You have the right to remain silent.

1558
02:01:36,913 --> 02:01:40,439
你有权请律师为你辩护
You have the right to an attorney during your interrogation.

1559
02:01:40,617 --> 02:01:44,905
你所说的任何话都会做为呈堂证供
Anything you say can and will be used against you in a court of law.

1560
02:01:45,088 --> 02:01:47,351
若你无法负担律师费用
If you cannot afford to hire a lawyer...

1561
02:01:47,524 --> 02:01:51,482
政府会在审问前，指派你的辩护律师
...one will be appointed to represent you if you wish one.

1562
02:02:04,306 --> 02:02:08,071
沙登探长，可否麻烦你待在这儿
Agent Sheldon, would you please remain on the apron...

1563
02:02:08,278 --> 02:02:11,701
直到所有人质都进入航站大厦为止？
...until the hostages are well inside the terminal?

1564
02:02:11,881 --> 02:02:12,938
重复
Repeat:

1565
02:02:13,116 --> 02:02:16,607
沙登探长，可否麻烦你待在这儿
Agent Sheldon, would you please remain on the apron...

1566
02:02:16,786 --> 02:02:21,176
直到所有人质都进入航站大厦为止？
...until the hostages are well inside the terminal?

1567
02:02:21,359 --> 02:02:23,724
是，我收到了，我们会守在这儿
Yeah, I got you. We'll hold here.

1568
02:03:07,805 --> 02:03:13,299
桑尼瓦基克在联邦监狱里服刑二十年

1569
02:03:13,477 --> 02:03:18,800
安祺瓦基克和她的小孩靠领福利金生活

1570
02:03:18,982 --> 02:03:24,442
礼昂谢摩现在已经变为女人，住在纽约市

